
Steps to create new repo

1.  Move to the working directory,
        cd /path/to/your/existing/code 
    Then run the below command;
        git init
        ls -a

2.  create new txt file and the content
        touch story1.txt 
        echo "This is a beautiful story" >> story1.txt

3.  Check the status using below command;
        git status
    Result;
        On branche Master
        No commits yet
        Untracked files;
        story1.txt
        nothing added to the commits but untracked files present

4.  Add tothe staging area using;
        git add story1.txt

5.  Commit files
        git commit -m "Added first story"



